SIMPLE: knowing
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Knowing
<hw>Know"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Skillful; well
informed; intelligent; <as>as, a <ex>knowing</ex> man; a
<ex>knowing</ex> dog.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>knowing</qex> and intelligent part of the world.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Artful; cunning; <as>as, a <ex>knowing</ex>
rascal</as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knowing</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Knowing
<hw>Know"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Knowledge; hence,
experience.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ In my <xex>knowing</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This sore night⟦br⟧
Hath trifled former <qex>knowings</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knowingly</ent>⟦br⟧
